front.title: •5D6-RA-7 (Fivedesix) (V)
front.gametext: Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. Power +1 while with your leader. If at a Scomp link when opponent draws a destiny of: 1-3, you may activate one Force; 4-6, you may draw top card of your Reserve Deck; 0 or 7 you may retrieve 1 Force.
front.lore: Aide to Admiral Motti's staff. Foul-tempered and vindictive. Feared by other droids. A spy for the ISB. Secretly investigates Imperial officers whose loyalties are in question.
